  "title": "SALES & MARKETING (ENTRY LEVEL) - NO EXP NEEDED ‼️",
  "description": "<p>This role is suitable for individuals who are looking to build a career in sales, marketing, and leadership. Fresh graduates, ORD personnel, and those exploring a career switch are welcome.<br /><br /><br />👀Who We Are Looking For<br />•  18 years old and above<br />• Singaporeans only<br />• No prior experience required (full training provided)<br />• Positive attitude with a willingness to learn and grow<br />• Comfortable working with people and in a team<br /><br />🤔What You Can Expect<br />• 1-to-1 mentorship with structured training<br />• Opportunities to develop communication and people skills<br />• Exposure to sales, marketing, and leadership responsibilities<br />• Clear career progression based on performance<br />• Supportive and friendly team environment<br />• Opportunities for regional and overseas exposure<br /><br /><br /><br />🫵🏽If you’re looking for more than just a job and want a role where you can grow, learn, and progress, we’d be happy to hear from you.🫵🏽<br /><br /><br /><br />Click APPPLY NOW or contact 8695 7302 [A’syura] (WhatsApp)/ aruyys_a (Telegram)</p>",
